00:10.070 --> 00:14.670
Setting up your niche Web site before you start getting excited about setting up your new niche Web

00:14.670 --> 00:15.040
site.

00:15.050 --> 00:19.970
You need to think about how you're going to get targeted visitor traffic to it in a later video we will

00:19.970 --> 00:21.880
discuss a number of ways that you can do this.

00:22.340 --> 00:26.880
But we want to start this video off by discussing SEO Search Engine Optimization.

00:27.020 --> 00:32.060
A lot of online marketers think that SEO is really too difficult these days with all of the changes

00:32.060 --> 00:35.190
that Google has made to its search engine algorithm.

00:35.190 --> 00:41.150
But this is a big mistake because it's actually easier to rank web pages now if they are optimized correctly.

00:41.150 --> 00:44.810
So the first thing you need to do is keyword research.

00:44.840 --> 00:48.530
The best niche websites start with comprehensive keyword research.

00:48.550 --> 00:53.000
We have already mentioned the google keyword planner and how you can use this to identify search volumes

00:53.000 --> 00:55.340
and related keywords for your niche.

00:55.340 --> 00:57.540
You need to take this a step further now.

00:57.730 --> 01:02.210
Unique Web site needs to be organized around the different types of keywords that you uncover.

01:02.210 --> 01:07.430
We recommend that you use the WordPress blogging platform for your niche Web site and it is very easy

01:07.430 --> 01:09.770
to set up different categories with this.

01:09.800 --> 01:13.120
This is what Google and the other search engines want you to do.

01:13.310 --> 01:17.380
So you want to generate a list of as many keywords for your list as you can.

01:17.390 --> 01:22.220
You're not going to rank your individual web pages for all these keywords but you certainly will for

01:22.220 --> 01:27.140
some of them as your Web site grows and becomes more of an authority then you will start to rank for

01:27.140 --> 01:29.510
some of more competitive terms.

01:29.540 --> 01:34.640
Think about the future now SEO is not a fast traffic solution but a long term one.

01:34.880 --> 01:39.740
You can get traffic to your niche Web site using other methods as your site develops but you always

01:39.740 --> 01:43.340
need to have SEO as the foundation of your niche Web site.

01:43.340 --> 01:47.630
Go to the google keyword planner and start by entering in your seed keyword.

01:47.630 --> 01:51.530
As we said before the planner will make suggestions for related keywords.

01:51.530 --> 01:55.930
You can then use these related keywords to find other related keywords.

01:56.000 --> 01:59.330
Set aside a few hours to create your initial list of keywords.

01:59.450 --> 02:03.350
It is not difficult to come up with hundreds of different keywords for your niche Web site.

02:03.380 --> 02:09.110
You can export the keywords that you find from the google keyword planner in CSP format and create Microsoft

02:09.110 --> 02:12.310
Excel or other format spreadsheets from this.

02:12.380 --> 02:15.260
These spreadsheets will be your mastered keyword lists.

02:15.350 --> 02:20.510
You will have a few to work keywords such as paleo diet some three word keywords such as paleo weight

02:20.510 --> 02:26.900
loss and quite a number of four and more keywords which will be your long tail keywords the long tail

02:26.900 --> 02:31.820
keywords will not have massive search volume but they will be a lot easier to rank for without too much

02:31.820 --> 02:32.770
effort.

02:32.780 --> 02:35.680
These will be the start of your free traffic from the search engines.

02:35.930 --> 02:40.130
Search engine traffic is the very best because it is really targeted.

02:40.130 --> 02:44.720
If someone is searching for paleo diet weight loss then this is very specific.

02:44.720 --> 02:48.170
They are truly interested in using the paleo diet to lose weight.

02:48.170 --> 02:52.220
Your web pages need to be in the search results for these kinds of terms so that you can provide the

02:52.220 --> 02:57.410
answers that people are looking for and either generate a new lead for your email list or make a sale

02:57.410 --> 02:58.800
or a commission.

02:58.850 --> 03:03.890
You need to understand that every keyword that you find will have a level of search engine competitiveness.

03:03.890 --> 03:08.030
Usually the higher the search volume the more competitive the keyword term will be.

03:08.030 --> 03:10.070
There are exceptions of course.

03:10.400 --> 03:14.910
If a keyword is very competitive it will take a very long time for you to rank high in Google and the

03:14.920 --> 03:16.480
other search engines for it.

03:16.610 --> 03:21.170
Personal terms such as paleo it will probably be impossible for you to rank on the first page for this

03:21.170 --> 03:22.720
no matter what you do.

03:22.880 --> 03:27.980
So you need to know how competitive the keywords in your list are and then determine how competitive

03:27.980 --> 03:29.090
they are.

03:29.090 --> 03:33.890
Please note that this is not the same as the competition column in the google keyword planner.

03:33.890 --> 03:37.780
This is the ads competition and will not be of any use to you.

03:37.820 --> 03:42.650
It is possible to make an assessment of keyword competition manually but this requires a lot of skill

03:42.650 --> 03:43.760
and time.

03:43.760 --> 03:46.240
Fortunately there are the ways you can do this.

03:46.250 --> 03:48.820
Here are the two methods that we recommend.

03:48.860 --> 03:55.520
