This is the range easy relatively easy medium difficult very difficult extremely difficult.

04:34.040 --> 04:38.540
Anything that is easy relatively easy or medium is fair game.

04:38.600 --> 04:40.380
The others will take a lot more work.

04:40.610 --> 04:44.150
