05:04.730 --> 05:07.100
than any of the other programs out there.

05:07.190 --> 05:11.810
It also has feature to measure keyword difficulty in a similar way to traffic Travis.

05:11.810 --> 05:16.550
The difference is that a refs has all of this information already stored so there is no waiting for

05:16.550 --> 05:17.680
the results.

