If you are serious about SEO then the monthly subscription prices start at ninety nine dollars a month.

05:23.420 --> 05:27.920
So to summarize you need a list of suitable keywords for your niche marketing site and you need to know

05:27.920 --> 05:31.010
the keyword difficulty or competition for each keyword.

05:31.070 --> 05:35.750
Then you can start to optimize your website and the content that you publish in line with this information

